data.description: Immerse yourself with simpler time in this historic Victorian/Eastlake home. Comfortable home with many original details. Tons of natural light and space w/ 5 bedrooms & 3 baths; formal living, foyer, and dining rooms; open kitchen with dining area and cozy keeping room. 5 fireplaces, soaring ceilings, transom windows, clawfoot tub, rocking chair front porch, rafter tails & bonus room. Fully landscaped with fenced private oasis for back yard, complete with covered patio and 3 sheds. HVAC 2019.
